text: Lyovino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Levinskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 321 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km south-east from Bolshaya Sosnova. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Lyovino
